{
  "stem": "2718.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But also we started to make-- to-- to have reports that that wasn't the last station, because it was sort of a transition camp, to-- to what we didn't know where to.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, at that time, our aim was to-- our only hope was to stay in-- in Hungary, and in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we-- we were hoping that we can stay in the ghetto, put it that way.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, most likely-- most likely I would say I was too young for that at that time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But most likely, I would say, it was what I heard were the-- were the German officers who came to-- daily, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because-- I'm sure it was so, because when it came to a crucial time when-- when people were started to be transported into these brick factory from the ghettos, they came-- the Germans came and said, look, you can stay.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You can go back to your houses, but not the family-- only the men.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Only-- only the-- the heads of the family-- my two uncles, my father, and my grandfather-- but the rest of the family has to stay in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Of course, there's no-- no need to say that they said, no, we're not going to be separated from our family.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We don't want to move back into our houses.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There's no point in it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We will-- we will go with out family, or stay with our family.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We'll move back to our houses if-- if our family moves back with us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I think after a very short time, it turned out that-- that the Hungarians had convinced the Germans that the people who were running the factory-- the foremen-- were-- were dispensable, so-- and-- and they didn't need them.",
      "word_count": 39
    }
  ],
